!TITLE
HUMAN OR ANIMAL?
!WORDS
The Associated Press released this news item under the dateline of 
Belfast, Northern Ireland: "Police have taken into custody a lad who 
has never been bathed, cannot eat human food, grunts like a beast, 
and roosts like a chicken.  A group of children playing hide-and-seek 
found him in the henhouse located behind a cottage occupied by a 
widow and her two grown daughters."  The headline introducing this 
article read: "FOUND BOY, 7, BROUGHT UP LIKE ANIMAL."
